<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida7d76d39-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s520b"><num value="520b">§ 520b.</num><heading> Applicants for enlistment: authority to use funds for the issue of authorized articles</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Funds appropriated to the Department of Defense may be used for the issue of authorized articles to applicants for enlistment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida7d76d3a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/98/525/tXIV/s1401/a/1">Pub. L. 98–525, title XIV, § 1401(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="1984-10-19">Oct. 19, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/2614">98 Stat. 2614</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/99/145/tXIII/s1303/a/4/A">Pub. L. 99–145, title XIII, § 1303(a)(4)(A)</ref>, <date date="1985-11-08">Nov. 8, 1985</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/99/738">99 Stat. 738</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
